https://zhaott0416.wordpress.com/2015/06/02/how-to-convert-fasta-files-to-nexus-files-in-r/

Using R Studio

> install.packages("seqinr")
> install.packages("ape")

> data = read.fasta("~/desktop/ncbi_dataset/atp6_gene_aln.fna")
> library(ape)
> write.nexus.data(data, file="~/desktop/ncbi_dataset/atp6_gene_aln.fna", format="dna")

> data = read.fasta("~/desktop/ncbi_dataset/cox1_gene_aln.fna")
> write.nexus.data(data, file="~/desktop/ncbi_dataset/cox1_gene_aln.fna", format="dna")
